{{ja-pos|interjection}}

# ''Used to call someone's attention to something;'' [[there]]!, [[look]]!
# ''Used to stir someone to action or fire oneself up;'' [[go on]]!, [[let's go]]!, [[right]]!, [[here goes]]!, [[come on]]!

===Usage notes===
*As an interjection, in sense 1, typically ''[[平板型|heiban]]'' pitch accent is used, where the second syllable is accented; while in sense 2, ''[[頭高型|atamadaka]]'' pitch accent is used, where the first syllable is accented and the second is not.

